
======================================================================
  bty USB live

  Read-only USB live boot of bty's CLI + flashing tools. Plug into
  a target machine, boot from this stick, run ``bty list disks`` /
  ``bty flash`` against the host's drives without touching the
  drive you booted from.

  Rootfs is ephemeral - any changes vanish on reboot (overlayroot).
